---
import LightLayout from '../layouts/LightLayout.astro';
---

<LightLayout title="龙虾科普 | 赚钱日记">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-12 relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-12">
    
    <!-- Sidebar Navigation -->
    <aside class="w-full md:w-64 lg:w-72 flex-shrink-0 order-2 md:order-1 hidden md:block">
      <div class="sticky top-28 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
        
        <!-- Progress Indicator -->
        <div class="mb-8">
           <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
             <span class="text-xs font-black text-gray-800 uppercase tracking-widest">5分钟速成进度</span>
             <span id="progressText" class="text-xs font-bold text-[#ca3d2f]">0%</span>
           </div>
           <div class="w-full bg-gray-100 rounded-full h-1.5 overflow-hidden">
              <div id="progressBar" class="bg-[#ca3d2f] h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out" style="width: 0%"></div>
           </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Table of Contents -->
        <nav class="space-y-1 border-l-2 border-gray-100 pl-4" id="toc">
           <a href="#chapter-1" class="toc-link block py-2 text-[14px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" data-target="chapter-1">1. 什么是龙虾？</a>
           <a href="#chapter-2" class="toc-link block py-2 text-[14px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" data-target="chapter-2">2. 龙虾能干什么？</a>
           <a href="#chapter-3" class="toc-link block py-2 text-[14px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" data-target="chapter-3">3. 怎么养一只龙虾？</a>
           <a href="#chapter-4" class="toc-link block py-2 text-[14px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" data-target="chapter-4">4. 团队怎么组建？</a>
           <a href="#chapter-5" class="toc-link block py-2 text-[14px] font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors" data-target="chapter-5">5. 怎么用龙虾赚钱？</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 order-1 md:order-2 pb-32">
      
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="text-5xl text-green-600 drop-shadow-sm">🔰</span> 龙虾速成指南
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          如果你还把 AI 当作聊天框，那你注定是被收割的一方。<br/>
          花 5 分钟看完这份指南，带你从“听说过”跨越到“拥有自己的一人军团”。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-24">
        
        <!-- Chapter 1 -->
        <section id="chapter-1" class="scroll-mt-32 chapter-section">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-black tracking-widest text-[#ca3d2f] mb-3 uppercase">Chapter 1</h2>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">什么是龙虾？</h3>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">ChatGPT 和龙虾的区别</h4>
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-700 font-bold text-[13px] rounded-lg mb-8">
              <span>💡</span> 一句话：ChatGPT是聊天框，龙虾是帮你干活的牛马员工
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <!-- ChatGPT side -->
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
                <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-500 mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span>🤖</span> 普通AI (ChatGPT等)
                </h5>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-[14px] text-gray-500">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-none">•</span> 你问它答，聊完就忘</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-none">•</span> 没有记忆，每次从头开始</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-none">•</span> 不能行动，只能给建议</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-none">•</span> 需要你一直盯着它打字</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Lobster side -->
              <div class="bg-green-50/30 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-green-400 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(34,197,94,0.1)] relative">
                <h5 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span>🦞</span> 龙虾 (AI Agent)
                </h5>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-[14px] text-gray-800 font-medium">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 text-lg leading-none">✓</span> 交代目标，它自动拆解并干活</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 text-lg leading-none">✓</span> 拥有长期向量记忆，认识你的客户</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 text-lg leading-none">✓</span> 能发推、写邮件、查数据并自己点击</li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 text-lg leading-none">✓</span> 7×24托管运行，你睡觉它收钱</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">一条极客世界的黄金配置公式</h4>
            
            <div class="text-center py-10 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 my-6">
              <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-gray-800 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 md:gap-4">
                <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">🤖 AI大脑</span> <span class="text-gray-300">+</span>
                <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">💻 独立系统</span> <span class="text-gray-300">+</span>
                <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">💾 记忆锚底</span> <span class="text-gray-300">+</span>
                <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">⚡️ 工具库</span> <span class="text-gray-300">=</span>
                <span class="text-white bg-[#ca3d2f] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg shadow-md tracking-widest">🦞 龙虾</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Chapter 2 -->
        <section id="chapter-2" class="scroll-mt-32 chapter-section">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-black tracking-widest text-[#ca3d2f] mb-3 uppercase">Chapter 2</h2>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">龙虾能干什么？</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5">📝</div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">内容全自动养号</h4>
              <p class="text-[14px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">自动抓取外网热点，重写排版，定时多账号分发到小红书、公众号和推特，批量培育私域流量池。</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-400 text-[11px] rounded font-mono">#脚本生成</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-400 text-[11px] rounded font-mono">#矩阵操作</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 text-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5">📊</div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">暗网与宏观数据监控</h4>
              <p class="text-[14px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">7x24小时刺探竞品价格，监控行业舆情。一旦特定关键词或商机出现，立刻在飞书/钉钉发警报推给你。</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-400 text-[11px] rounded font-mono">#价格爬虫</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-400 text-[11px] rounded font-mono">#商机截流</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5">🤖</div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">销售闭环与智能客服</h4>
              <p class="text-[14px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">通过 MCP 对接微信，自动识别恶意砍价，并抛出话术截流；客户付款后自动调用发货接口，完成纯躺赚。</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-400 text-[11px] rounded font-mono">#全托管</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-50 text-gray-400 text-[11px] rounded font-mono">#私域成交</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Chapter 3 -->
        <section id="chapter-3" class="scroll-mt-32 chapter-section">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-black tracking-widest text-[#ca3d2f] mb-3 uppercase">Chapter 3</h2>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">怎么养一只龙虾？</h3>
          </div>

          <!-- Server Requirements -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm mb-8">
            <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-100 pb-4">📋 服务器要求</h4>

            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                    <th class="text-left py-3 font-black text-gray-900">配置项</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-3 font-black text-gray-900">推荐规格</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-3 font-black text-gray-900">推荐服务商</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-gray-600">
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                    <td class="py-3 font-medium">操作系统</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Ubuntu 22.04 LTS</td>
                    <td class="py-3 text-green-600">必选</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                    <td class="py-3 font-medium">CPU</td>
                    <td class="py-3">2核心</td>
                    <td class="py-3" rowspan="3" valign="top">Hetzner / AWS Lightsail / 腾讯云</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-50">
                    <td class="py-3 font-medium">内存</td>
                    <td class="py-3">4GB</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-3 font-medium">存储</td>
                    <td class="py-3">40GB SSD</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 font-bold text-sm mb-1">
                <span>💰</span> 预估月费用
              </div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-green-600">约 ¥35/月</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-green-600/70 mt-1">$5/月起的云服务器即可跑满全负荷</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Real Installation Steps -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm mb-8">
            <h4 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 border-b border-gray-100 pb-4">🚀 五步极简部署法（官方一键安装）</h4>

            <div class="space-y-6 relative before:absolute before:inset-0 before:ml-5 before:-translate-x-px md:before:mx-auto md:before:translate-x-0 before:h-full before:w-0.5 before:bg-gradient-to-b before:from-transparent before:via-gray-200 before:to-transparent">

              <!-- Step 1 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-4 border-white bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 font-black shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 group-[.is-active]:bg-[#ca3d2f] group-[.is-active]:text-white z-10">1</div>
                <div class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-3rem)] bg-gray-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900">准备 Telegram Bot</h5>
                  <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 mt-2">在 Telegram 搜索 @BotFather，创建新机器人并保存 Token。同时获取你的用户ID备用。</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 2 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-4 border-white bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 font-black shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 group-[.is-active]:bg-[#ca3d2f] group-[.is-active]:text-white z-10">2</div>
                <div class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-3rem)] bg-gray-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900">准备 AI 模型访问</h5>
                  <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 mt-2">方案A：有 Claude Pro/Max 订阅 → OAuth 登录<br>方案B：无订阅 → console.anthropic.com 创建 API Key</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 3 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-4 border-white bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 font-black shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 group-[.is-active]:bg-[#ca3d2f] group-[.is-active]:text-white z-10">3</div>
                <div class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-3rem)] bg-gray-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900">一键安装命令</h5>
                  <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 mt-2">在服务器终端执行以下命令，自动安装所有依赖：</p>
                  <div class="mt-3 bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs overflow-x-auto">
                    curl -fsSL https://openclaw.ai/install.sh | bash
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 4 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-4 border-white bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 font-black shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 group-[.is-active]:bg-[#ca3d2f] group-[.is-active]:text-white z-10">4</div>
                <div class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-3rem)] bg-gray-50 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Wizard 配置向导</h5>
                  <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 mt-2">交互式配置：选择 AI 模型 → 粘贴 Telegram Token → 设置管理员 → 安装后台服务</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 5 -->
              <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group is-active">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-4 border-white bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 font-black shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 group-[.is-active]:bg-[#ca3d2f] group-[.is-active]:text-white z-10">5</div>
                <div class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-3rem)] bg-[#ca3d2f]/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-[#ca3d2f]/20">
                  <h5 class="font-bold text-[#ca3d2f]">启动并验证</h5>
                  <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-600 mt-2">运行 <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">openclaw gateway --port 18789</code>，在 Telegram 发送消息测试</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Common Commands -->
          <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-lg mb-8">
            <h4 class="font-black text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>⌨️</span> 日常管理命令
            </h4>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 font-mono text-xs">
              <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2">检查整体状态</div>
                <div class="text-green-400">openclaw status</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2">检查网关状态</div>
                <div class="text-green-400">openclaw gateway status</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2">健康检查</div>
                <div class="text-green-400">openclaw health</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2">查看运行日志</div>
                <div class="text-green-400">openclaw daemon logs</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2">重启后台服务</div>
                <div class="text-green-400">openclaw daemon restart</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-gray-400 mb-2">重新配置</div>
                <div class="text-green-400">openclaw configure</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ Section -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
             <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
               <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">
                 不会敲代码也能养吗？
                 <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-gray-400 text-xl">+</span>
               </summary>
               <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-[14px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-50 pt-4 mt-1">
                 完全可以。官方提供一键安装脚本 <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded">curl -fsSL https://openclaw.ai/install.sh | bash</code>，会自动处理所有依赖（Node.js、Git等），你只需要按照向导提示输入配置即可。10 分钟即可完成部署。
               </div>
             </details>
             <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
               <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">
                 养这套系统每个月花多少钱？
                 <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-gray-400 text-xl">+</span>
               </summary>
               <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-[14px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-50 pt-4 mt-1">
                 <ul class="space-y-2">
                   <li>• 服务器：约 ¥35/月 (Hetzner $5/月)</li>
                   <li>• AI API 调用费用：约 ¥30-100/月（按实际使用量）</li>
                   <li>• 总计：<strong class="text-green-600">¥65-135/月</strong></li>
                 </ul>
               </div>
             </details>
             <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
               <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-5 font-bold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">
                 Node.js 版本过低怎么办？
                 <span class="transition group-open:rotate-45 text-gray-400 text-xl">+</span>
               </summary>
               <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-[14px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-50 pt-4 mt-1">
                 <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs mb-2">node -v  # 检查版本，需要 Node 22+</div>
                 <div class="text-gray-500">如需升级：</div>
                 <div class="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs mt-2">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.0/install.sh | bash && nvm install 22</div>
               </div>
             </details>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Chapter 4 -->
        <section id="chapter-4" class="scroll-mt-32 chapter-section">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-black tracking-widest text-[#ca3d2f] mb-3 uppercase">Chapter 4</h2>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">龙虾团队怎么组建？</h3>
          </div>

